---
// index.astro
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Fishnini Tents – Magical Outdoor Glamping</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      header {
        background: url('/hero-bg.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
        height: 100vh;
        color: white;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 2rem;
      }
      header h1 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      header p {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        max-width: 600px;
      }
      section {
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: auto;
      }
      .btn {
        background: #fff;
        color: #000;
        padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 6px;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
      }
      .card {
        background: #f9f9f9;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      }
      footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2rem;
        background: #222;
        color: #fff;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <header>
      <h1>Welcome to Fishnini Tents</h1>
      <p>Glamping tents that turn ordinary nights into magical experiences. Weddings, festivals, retreats – we’ve got you covered.</p>
      <a class="btn" href="#contact">Book Now</a>
    </header>

    <section>
      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>
        Fishnini is all about creating unforgettable outdoor stays. Whether you're planning a rustic wedding, a weekend retreat with friends,
        or a boutique festival, our luxurious bell tents offer the perfect blend of comfort and style. We handle everything – from setup to pack-down – so you can focus on enjoying the moment.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Our Services</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Wedding Tents</h3>
          <p>Make your special day even more memorable with dreamy canvas tents for your guests or private honeymoon hideaways.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Festival Glamping</h3>
          <p>Forget the muddy sleeping bags. Arrive to a fully set-up tent with proper beds, lights, and cozy decorations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Retreat Packages</h3>
          <p>Perfect for yoga retreats or corporate escapes. Custom layouts and decor to match your event vibe.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Gallery</h2>
      <div class="grid">
        <img src="/tent1.jpg" alt="Tent 1" style="width:100%; border-radius: 8px;" />
        <img src="/tent2.jpg" alt="Tent 2" style="width:100%; border-radius: 8px;" />
        <img src="/tent3.jpg" alt="Tent 3" style="width:100%; border-radius: 8px;" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>Email: hello@fishnini.com</p>
      <p>Phone: +1 (555) 123-4567</p>
      <a class="btn" href="mailto:hello@fishnini.com">Send Email</a>
    </section>

    <footer>
      <p>© 2025 Fishnini Tents. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

  </body>
</html>
